ult of ~1000 (90% confidence interval of 110-3840)\nGpc$^{-3}$yr$^{-1}$ by gravitational-wave detection, and a few events per\nGpc$^3$ per year of cBHNSs associated with r-process production are predicted\nto emerge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Dec 2019 19:11:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-12"}
