amics via self-injection locking, as well as\nthe repetition rate evolution, experimentally. We reveal that Kerr nonlinearity\nin microresonator significantly modifies locking dynamics, making laser\nemission frequency red detuned. We propose and implement a novel technique for\nmeasurements of the nonlinear frequency tuning curve and concurrent observation\nof microcomb states switching in real time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Dec 2019 11:49:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Jan 2020 07:43:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 26 Mar 2020 13:17:41 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 13 May 2020 11:35:40 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 20 Nov 2020 11:48:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
